{"tid":880831,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【樊少皇俾好友出賣】借錢俾人反被指欠債 賈曉晨：已經報咗警","createTime":"2018-10-29T03:51:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T06:31:35.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a0e28a7f11e699b9b462c2d464f49bec091198e5","tid":880831,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T03:51:31.000Z","msg":"JJ賈曉晨今晚出席電影《失蹤》煞科宴，喺電影中飾演CID嘅JJ，戲中除咗有開槍鏡頭外，仲有動作戲份，JJ表示拍之前亦有相約女警朋友見面：「發現佢哋身上的確有男子氣概，所以對於我嚟講係好大挑戰，因為拍完要番屋企湊女，唔可以咁惡，要變番女仔。」<br />\n囡囡「小飯兜」唔經唔覺已11個月大，問佢識叫爸爸媽媽未？JJ就話：「仲未，依家佢只係識叫『奶、奶』同自己個名『兜兜』，不過佢已經戒咗人奶，B女好大食、好大隻，依家都成12kg，身型好似人哋歲幾嘅小朋友咁，可能BB骨架方面似Daddy，又眼大大咁。」<br />\nJJ指因為老公樊少皇經常唔係屋企，所以會因為想陪囡囡多啲而少接工作，問佢有冇打算幾時追多個，佢就話：「遲啲先，想做吓嘢先，依家嘅生活都集中喺北京，但若然返香港拍嘢都會帶埋BB一齊，不過今次番嚟就冇帶，喺街見到BB都會好掛住個女，平時如果要離開都會唔捨得，阿女依家都知，平時我要出去做嘢，佢都會拉住我，我都覺得好心痛。」<br />\n提到早前樊少皇被匿名信追債200萬（相關新聞： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2CKsTLA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2CKsTLA&d=w7SRCe7k2aCBnNsguPYfLC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=abe003bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2CKsTLA</a> ）， JJ話：「其實好無辜，係佢俾人借咗幾百萬，人哋冇還俾佢，反而令佢俾人追債，已經報咗警落案同交咗俾律師處理，而CID亦都跟進緊，之後都會搵律師去追番筆錢，其實都好慘，今次係由細玩到大嘅朋友令到佢（樊少皇）名譽同金錢受損失，係傷心嘅事。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181028/large/1540732450_5d2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181028%2Flarge%2F1540732450_5d2b.jpg&h=fa02586c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181028/large/1540732594_b34e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181028%2Flarge%2F1540732594_b34e.jpg&h=da275d3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181028/58846952\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181028%2F58846952&d=w7SRCe7k2aCBnNsguPYfLC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=18a8e205\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181028%2F58846952&h=08bd45df\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181028/58846952</a>"},{"pid":"7e5577cb0127be7dfbd12531d87dae17df9b7d31","tid":880831,"uid":71071,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T04:02:18.000Z","msg":"小飯兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解個個明星仔女都要叫蝦餃燒賣义燒包鷄札？"},{"pid":"32047bd1ada680eaa4d6139280d0f602f2d0e85e","tid":880831,"uid":68,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T04:04:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>撕開d皮</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"89e93d603f3891f55cfb3c283d1ca5d12a2bbe13","tid":880831,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T04:06:09.000Z","msg":"jj真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0b0b7634387d05d6ba6bed0ae7942789f18c3a","tid":880831,"uid":59711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T04:14:13.000Z","msg":"JJ真係好好J,啱啱出道果陣屌打曬同期果d女明星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a8f5bb0ae81714b1d79e5950a1e1e1bcef72d14","tid":880831,"uid":28786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T04:16:36.000Z","msg":"已經冇人討論佢老公比人呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8da40701dd8b73f5122aea92d74b30b6d1ed139","tid":880831,"uid":98386,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T04:17:20.000Z","msg":"你個仆街老公都唔係乜好人啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe5d3f78fe05031fad080660704a3dafce84cf2","tid":880831,"uid":42435,"like":0,"